    "Human judgment simply does not operate at this scale.",
    "Content moderation on the Internet therefore mostly does not operate through human decisionmaking, but instead through the application of Artificial Intelligence (AI).\").",
    "42 See Saar Alon-Barkat & Madalina Busuioc, Human-AI Interactions in Public Sector Decision Making: \"Automation Bias\" and \"Selective Adherence\" to Algorithmic Advice, 33 J. PUB.",
    "& THEORY 153, 153 (2022) (\"These development [in AI] are driven by the promise of policy solutions that are potentially more effective, efficient, and low-cost.\").",
